name: Ethereal
description: Ethereal 1a: of or relating to the regions beyond the earth b: CELESTIAL, HEAVENLY c: UNWORLDLY, SPIRITUAL 2a: lacking material substance : IMMATERIAL, INTANGIBLE b: marked by unusual delicacy or refinement this smallest, most ethereal, and daintiest of birds — William Beebe c: suggesting the heavens or heaven 3: relating to, containing, or resembling a chemical ether
